ticket.title: CookieStore does not implement backwards compatibility for :session_domain
ticket.original-body:
In cookie_store.rb (2.3.5), there is support for backwards compatibility of several keys:
# Process legacy CGI options options = options.symbolize_keys if options.has_key?(:session_path) options[:path] = options.delete(:session_path) end if options.has_key?(:session_key) options[:key] = options.delete(:session_key) end if options.has_key?(:session_http_only) options[:httponly] = options.delete(:session_http_only) end
But there is no support for :session_domain. Should this be added for completeness sake?
if options.has_key?(:session_domain) options[:domain] = options.delete(:session_domain) end
